flowchart TD
  Source[Repository source] --> Maven[Maven package]
  Maven --> Jar[TenantService.jar]
  Jar --> Docker[Dockerfile image]
  Docker --> K3s[k3s image import]
  K3s --> Rollout[Kubernetes rollout restart]
  Config[application*.properties and environment] --> Validator[ConfigurationValidator]
  Validator --> App[Spring Boot TenantService]
  DB[(MariaDB)] --> App
  Keycloak[Keycloak JWT issuer] --> App
  Services[ORISO service URLs] --> App
